    "GRMHD: A snapshot from a GRMHD simulation of M87 *.",
    "The synthetic visibilities were generated using eht-imaging and all include random thermal noise, stationbased gain and phase errors, and polarimetric leakage.",
    "For a more in-depth explanation of synthetic visibility generation, we refer readers to Appendix C.2 of M 87 * 2017 IV.",
    "Figures G.2 and G.3 show the image reconstructions for four training and seven validation data sets including the GRMHD model from each imaging pipeline, respectively.",
